   About

Farm2KitchenBlockchain for Food Traceability

   Farm2Kitchen® is building the first technology platform of its kind for
   the Food Supply Chain- which will be a Global Food Marketplace, A
   Farmers Network while providing food traceability along the whole
   supply chain. By utilizing the Blockchain technology of distributed
   ledger and smart contracts to uniquely track every step of the food
   delivery on a shared ledger in order to ensure transparency, Food
   Safety and provide the foundation for sustainable agricultural growth
   and food security.
     * Food Traceability
     * Global Farmers Marketplace
     * Food Security

